connectorRef.description: Localhost OpenDJ for test generic synchronization

expression.description: Expression that assigns a fixed description value if there is no other description present.

script.code:
import javax.naming.ldap.Rdn import javax.naming.ldap.LdapName
dn = new LdapName('ou=groups,dc=example,dc=com') dn.add(new Rdn('cn', name.toString())) return dn.toString()

correlation.q:description: Correlation expression is a search query. Following search query will look for users that have "name" equal to the "uid" attribute of the account. Simply speaking, it will look for match in usernames in the IDM and the resource. The correlation rule always looks for users, so it will not match any other object type.
